description: Best practices for integrating AWS Cognito with React Native applications
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}
---

- Use AWS Amplify for simplified integration with Cognito
- Implement secure authentication flows (e.g., OAuth, SAML)
- Store tokens securely using AsyncStorage or SecureStore
- Handle user sessions and token refresh logic effectively
- Use multi-factor authentication (MFA) for enhanced security
- Monitor and log authentication events for debugging and analytics